- Bugs in edit mode where squashed.

0.2 - 2021-09-09
- Limit increased to text files with 1568 lines and 80 columns - almost all the MSX 2 VRAM.
- Some nasty bugs squashed.

0.1 - 2021-09-04
- First public release.
- Almost all routines runs smoothly.
- Limited to text files with 346 lines with 80 columns each.